  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About February of '48.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went from New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We caught a train across-- we stopped over in Chicago and then finished up in San Francisco, and then flew from San Francisco to Sydney.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Pan Am Clipper.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Took three days.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very depressing, if truth be told.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as far as I was concerned, I went from a normal household, where I lived in a small country town in the United States, with-- with my aunt and uncle and his three daughters.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had boyfriends and cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to take me everywhere, because my aunt insisted on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were teenagers or early in their 20s, and they didn't want me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I insisted that I had to be taken everywhere-- to the movies, to see Humphrey Bogart movies and all that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was really great.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I was back-- well, not back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was in this city, living in a little hotel called the Kirketon Hotel, at the Cross, which was a very dingy place and not knowing anybody.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after a week, we were thrown out, because it was the Easter Show, and they had-- the hotel was booked out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that my parents couldn't understand why, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Having lived in Paris, which, which is a bit more sophisticated, why, after just one week, we are thrown out when we are willing to pay for staying there?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the reason was there was few in the way of-- very few rooms there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were all taken up by the Easter Show.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
